1. Permissions

You are hereby granted permission to:

Download and use Meowtils for personal use.

Decompile or inspect the source code to verify functionality, understand features, or analyze how the code works and interacts with your game.

Create your own derivative works of Meowtils for personal use only.

Create and distribute separate mods that interact with Meowtils classes, modify or extend its features, provided:
- They do not modify Meowtils' original JAR file.
- They are clearly marked as unofficial and separate from Meowtils.

Distribute official, unmodified versions of Meowtils, provided no changes or additions have been made to the original code or assets.

2. Restrictions

You may not:

Distribute modified versions of Meowtils, or tools/patches whose primary purpose is to alter Meowtils original code or assets. This does not restrict distribution of separate modifications for Meowtils that may modify it at runtime without modifying the original JAR file.

Use any portion of the source code, assets, or resources from Meowtils in any project intended for public distribution without explicit written permission from the author.

Sell, monetize, or otherwise profit from distributing Meowtils or any modified/derivative version thereof, including but not limited to paywalls, ad-based links, or inclusion in paid modpacks.

